thread.title: Jennifer
thread.title_full: Rubber Stamp Champ reviewed by Jennifer

author: Jennifer
title: Jennifer
text: I love my rubber stamp! It was easy to navigate and use the website to design, order and pay for my stamp. The price is very reasonable and it was a pleasure working with this company. I received my custom order very quickly and shipping rates were reasonable. I would gladly use this company again and recommend them to anyone!
